{
  "stem": "19550.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we arrived in, in the morning in Auschwitz [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] to-- again, this is very interesting, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "To us, it all seemed total chaos and disarray.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, we were pouring out of the railroad cars by the thousands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were, you know, maybe a half a dozen SS men with dogs hanging around, but there were-- and there were these peculiar people with the striped suits rushing around and shouting, get out and out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, and the dogs were barking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, and it all seemed like total chaos, and yet the Germans had very good order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Without even knowing, they were separating men and women, you know, without-- we, we didn't even realize it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't have a chance to realize it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It all went like a well-oiled machine, even though that to us it looked chaotic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And these funny-looking striped people would drop a word here and a word there or motion, you're going up into smoke.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when you tried to hang on to something that you had brought, because they would tear it out of your hand and take it away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they would, they would tell you, you're as good as dead, and all sorts of hints, drops, outright statements, and it all had to be done in, in seconds, because before you knew it, you were, you were already ten paces away.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You were being shoved and pushed [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] all towards one, one goal, towards Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You were just being literally pushed without your awareness of where you were going or why you were going.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
